<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Greater Harvest</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
3 skill points, 3 levels +3 each up (3/6/9 to max) - Activated, 10-15 Minute ReUse<br>
<br>
Turns the Harvest spell into a skill button freeing up a spell slot, it also shares the same timer as Harvest so both cannot be used.  There are three levels to this skill...<br>
<br>
Level 1: Returns 301 mana, 10 second stun, 10 minute reuse.<br>
Level 2: Returns 508 mana, 12 second stun, 12 minute reuse.<br>
Level 3: Returns 1016 mana, 15 second stun, 15 minute reuse.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Improved Concussion</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
5 skill points, 1 level - Automatic.<br>
<br>
Turns &quot;Spell:Concussion&quot; into an unresistable spell.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Arcane Knowledge</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
3 skill points, 3 levels +3 each up (3/6/9 to max) - Activated, 5 Minute ReUse<br>
<br>
Level 1: Detects your enemies weakness to Fire based spells.<br>
Level 2: Detects your enemies weakness to Ice based spells.<br>
Level 3: Detects your enemies weakness to Magic based spells.<br>
<br>
Assume I used this ability Phara Dar, the returned data would look like this...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Rombus eyes his opponent and searches for their subtle flaws...<br>
Phara Dar has a strong resistance to Fire based spells.<br>
Phara Dar has a moderate resistance to Ice based spells.<br>
Phara Dar is immune to Magic based spells.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
Anyway.. those are my ideas!  Feel free to toss in your own. <p><br>
