<br>
Melee strikes pass right through the wizard with no damage. Triggered class skill. Reuse timer once per EQ day. Wizard is stunned for the duration of Phase Shift and an additional 5 seconds afterward. (PvP servers might need to drop the stun component for this to be useful)<br>
<br>
Level 1: 5 seconds<br>
Level 2: 8 seconds<br>
Level 3: 15 seconds<br>
<br>
A wizard_01's body shimmers and disperses.<br>
A wizard_01's body solidifies. <br>
<br>
==============================================<br>
<br>
Sorcerer's Frenzy<br>
<br>
For a limited time all spells cast by the wizard will in effect cast twice, cost twice the mana and double all damage including criticals. Wizard takes a hit on stamina and is silenced for a duration equal to frenzy afterwards. However, right click items may be used.<br>
<br>
Level 1: 15 second use with 1 reuse per EQ week<br>
Level 2: 22 second use with 1 reuse per 4 EQ days<br>
Level 3: 30 second use with 1 reuse per 2 EQ days<br>
<br>
A wizard_01 goes into a frenzy of spellcasting.<br>
A wizard_01 collapses, exhausted from his frenzy.<br>
<br>
==============================================<br>
<br>
Mana Store<br>
<br>
Class ability to store mana in a component(I.E. Burned out lightstone). Reuse time is immediate, but drains 750 mana over 10 seconds and stuns the wizard an additional 5 seconds. Can only be done while meditating. Results in a lore no-drop item Orb of Stored Mana - right click effect restore mana, instantaneous, increase mana by 500. Orb of Stored Mana poofs upon use.<br>
<br>
A wizard_01 enters a trance-like state.<br>
A wizard_01 calls upon his stored mana.<br>
<br>
==============================================<br>
<br>
Aura of the Masters<br>
<br>
Level 1: O'Keils Firy Aura adds fire resist(10), fire damage sheild(5), and increases dodge ability(15).<br>
Level 2: Solist's Icy Aura adds cold resist(10), cold damage shield(5), and increases dodge ability(15).<br>
Level 3: Elnerick's Electric Aura adds magic resist(10), magic damage shield(5), and increases dodge ability(15).<br>
<br>
Each level adds ring of appropriate graphic around the wizard, making it harder to actually see the wizard inside the ring. Ability can be toggled off for viewing equipment graphics, but must be toggled back on for battle. Wizard is stunned for 10 seconds while transforming his aura from one type to the other, can only be done while meditating.<br>
<br>
A wizard_01 calls upon the ancient masters for protection.<br>
A wizard_01 releases his Aura of the Masters.<br>
 <br>
