<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Innate swimming</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - Raises your swimming speed by 5, 10, and 20%.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Innate vision</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - Increase your visual perception. <br>
Infravision = 2 points<br>
Ultravision = 3 points<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Class Abilites (Level 59+)</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Extended Range</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - Increases spell range to target by 5, 10, and 20%.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Extended Area Range</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - Increases area effect range by 10, 20, and 30%.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Superior Gate</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - Allows the wizard to instantly gate to their bindpoint.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Racial Abilities (Level 54+)</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Dark Elves</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Innate Hide</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill will increase your ability to hide by 5, 10, and 20%.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Erudites</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Mental Superiority</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - Increases the Erudites intelligence by 2, 4, and 8 points.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Gnomes</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Tinkering Mastery</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill will increase the gnomes tinkering skill by 5, 10, and 20%.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  High Elf</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Righteousness</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - Increases base faction to all groups by 1 level. (If at max KoS, this ability would raise you to threatening).<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Humans</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Combine Sense</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This ability allows a Human to gate/translocate/teleport to any of the large combine spires for a reduced mana cost (5, 10, and 20%).<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Religious Abilities (level 56+)</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Redemption</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - Increases faction with your deity by 1 level per point. (If you're at max negative faction, 3 points into this skill would bring you to dubious with your god and their followers.)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Bertoxxulous' Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This ability raises the players disease resistance by 5, 10, and 20 points.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Brell Serilis's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This ability raises the players defensive abilities by 5, 10, and 20% while in underground areas.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Bristlebane's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill raises the players ability to beg by 10, 20, and 30%.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Cazic-Thule's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill allows the player a 5, 10, and 20% chance at resisting fear spells.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Innoruuk's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill allows the player a 5, 10, and 20% chance to resist life tap spells.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Karana's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill allows the player to see more clearly in bad weather conditions (5, 10, and 20%).<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Erollisi's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill allows the player a 5, 10, and 20% chance at charming NPCs less than 25 levels below them.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Mithaniel's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill gives the player a permanent faction boost with all good races by 1, 2, and 3 faction levels.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Prexus's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill gives the player extended breathing underwater. (20%, 40%, and permanent).<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Quellious's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill allows the player a 5, 10, and 20% chance at resisting fear spells.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Rodcet Nife's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill gives the player additional regeneration by 1, 3, and 6 points.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Solusek Ro's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This ability raises the players Fire resistance by 5, 10, and 20 points.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  The Tribunal's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill gives the player a permanent faction boost with all good races by 1, 2, and 3 faction levels.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Tunare's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This skill gives the player a permanent faction boost with all animals by 1, 2, and 3 faction levels.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Rallos Zek's Touch</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> - This ability raises the players offensive abilities by 5, 10, and 15%.<br>
<br>
